{"tid":1672082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英領館外千人集會 求獲國籍","createTime":"2019-10-24T01:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T02:00:35.000Z","uid":56881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"241a6d218d07491581254ec738c28cea51236c89","tid":1672082,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E5%A4%96%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E6%B1%82%E7%8D%B2%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D-214500257.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B1%258D-214500257.html&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=bec6e190\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E5%A4%96%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E6%B1%82%E7%8D%B2%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D-214500257.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvixkk5Xdy_7SrQUsvzGEA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/cb69d07c187d8bd309c1c0ad2dc7e43e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNvixkk5Xdy_7SrQUsvzGEA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fcb69d07c187d8bd309c1c0ad2dc7e43e&h=d66b6a56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n集會人士手持英國旗及港英旗。（黃偉邦攝）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反修例風波撼動港人對香港前途的信心，有市民昨晚自發於英國領事館組成英國旗人鏈，聲援英國上議院議員奧爾頓勳爵（Lord Alton）將於倫敦時間24日在上議院進行兩個半小時辯論，為港人爭取第二國籍。有集會人士認為，英國對香港有其道義責任作出援助。<br />\n<br />\n人鏈企滿正義道半山至法院道，部分人手持英國國旗。<br />\n<br />\n揮英國旗呼口號<br />\n<br />\n大會在人鏈開始前播出英國國歌，期間有人高舉BNO護照，高呼「Fight for freedom, stand with Hong Kong」、「One country two system is dead」等口號。持有BNO護照的洪先生認為，香港作為國際城市，需得到國際支持，而且英國對香港有道義責任。<br />\n<br />\n手持英國旗的關小姐則指，撤回修例是不足夠，會繼續參與抗爭活動。大會公布，參與人鏈的人數達一千五百人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a368014cf86611bd4d299a45de3e7c0d59ecaa6","tid":1672082,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:00:35.000Z","msg":"簽咗未？<br />\n<br />\n爭取完整英國國籍<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/275360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F275360&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=b6823f9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/275360</a><br />\n<br />\n[CANZUK] 爭取將BN(O)納入英國同澳洲嘅Freedom of Movement + 公平對待BN(O)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aph.gov.au/petition_list?id=EN1067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aph.gov.au%2Fpetition_list%3Fid%3DEN1067&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=8bec293e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aph.gov.au/petition_list?id=EN1067</a><br />\n<br />\n[美帝] 爭取Visa Waiver Program免簽 + 方便BN(O)入境美國申請庇護 + 視BN(O)等同BC<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/visa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fvisa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=ad476f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/visa-waiver-program-vwp-should-be-given-british-national-overseas</a>"}]}